  "summary": {
    "macroSummary": "Markets are caught between escalating US-Iran tensions that support dollar/oil/volatility and emerging ceasefire hopes that are driving risk-on flows into crypto and risk assets. The geopolitical binary is creating whipsaw price action with BTC breaking above $69K on short squeezes while traditional safe havens like gold decline on ceasefire speculation.",
