    "actionItems": [
      "Monitor BMNR ladder closely as BTC approaches $70K resistance with elevated leverage in ETH derivatives signaling potential volatility",
      "Prepare to add short exposure if oil retreats significantly on ceasefire confirmation, breaking the stagflation narrative",
      "Maintain Maturity sector overweight as rising 10Y yields amid geopolitical stress favor defensive positioning"
    ],
    "keySignals": [
      "BTC surge past $69K with $196M shorts liquidated suggests momentum but needs to clear $70K for regime change confirmation.",
      "Oil weakness on ceasefire hopes could break stagflation thesis if sustained below $100.",
      "Rising 10Y yields amid geopolitical tensions approaching the critical 4.50% growth stress level.",
      "Dollar strength above DXY 100 supporting the bear market relief rally rather than new bull cycle thesis."
